# EasyOrders custom themes — مرجع عملي

**المصدر الرسمي:** [Custom Themes](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/category/custom-themes) · [Getting Started](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/getting-started) · [Palette](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/palette) · [Dynamic Theme Data](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/dynamic-theme-data) · [Liquid Reference](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/liquid-reference) · [Events & Data Attributes](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/events-reference) · [Layout](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/sections/layout-sections) · [Product](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/sections/product-sections) · [Home](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/sections/home-sections) · [Utility](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/sections/utility-sections)

**محرك القوالب:** [LiquidJS](https://liquidjs.com/) — كل `.liquid` يُعرض مع بيانات المتجر في السياق.

---

## 1) ما هو الثيم المخصص

- **Liquid** (20 ملف في `sections/`) + **`style.css`** + **`script.js`** + **`schema.json`**
- CSS/JS يُحمَّلان على **كل** الصفحات (غالباً بعد minify عند الرفع)
- أسماء ملفات `sections/` **ثابتة** — الرفع path-based
- مرجع بداية: [Getting Started — Allbirds example](https://themes-docs.easy-orders.net/docs/custom-themes/getting-started)

```text
my-theme/
├── sections/     ← 20 قسم منصة
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── schema.json
```

كل قسم `.liquid` يستقبل متغيرات المنصة + **`theme_data`** من `schema.json` تلقائياً.

